name: Die with the most likes dies at Rally’s in Northern Indiana
description: Our collective Consciousnesses is shoved through a barely functioning meat grinder at the hands of the myth, transforming what little memories we have left into a sickening burger blend, and spoon fed to barely sentient corpses looking to fuel themselves through another miserable day. we are all beef. we are all consumed. with hopes of one day emerging from dying organs and birthing into the polluted river flowing through town
